ğŸ“± Synchronous ChatApp

A real-time MERN chat application I built to explore Socket.io, authentication flows, and modern UI design. The goal was to recreate a WhatsApp-style chatting experience with instant messaging, clean visuals, and smooth state handling.

ğŸ”— Frontend: https://synchronous-chatapp.vercel.app

ğŸ”— Backend: https://synchronous-chatapp-3npb.onrender.com

ğŸš€ What I built

Secure login/signup using JWT + cookies

Real-time one-to-one messaging (Socket.io)

Contact list with last message preview

File & media upload (profile pictures + attachments)

Channel/group chat support

Responsive UI with Tailwind + Shadcn

Readable timestamps, icons, animations, and smooth transitions

MongoDB aggregation for efficient data fetching

Socket-based user presence tracking

ğŸ§° Tech I used
Frontend

React, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn/UI, Redux Toolkit, Context API, RTK Query, Axios, Lottie, Lucide-react

Backend

Node.js, Express.js, Socket.io, JWT, Cookie-parser, CORS

Database

MongoDB Atlas (with aggregation pipelines)

